---
title: Chocolate Cake
description: A classic and delicious chocolate cake recipe with rich cocoa flavor.
---

Preheat oven to 350Â°F. Cream @butter{1%cup} and @sugar{2%cup} together until light and fluffy.

Beat in @eggs{3} one at a time, ensuring each is fully incorporated before adding the next.

Mix @flour{2%cup} and @cocoa{1%cup} together in a separate bowl.

Fold the flour mixture gently into the wet ingredients until just combined.

Pour into a greased pan and bake for 35-40 minutes until a toothpick inserted in the center comes out clean.
